delete

public boolean delete(java.lang.String isbn)
Deletes the record with the specified primary keys. The point of this api is to prevent a hit on the db to see if the record is there. This call will add a record to the next transaction that is marked for delete.

Returns:
Returns true if the record was previous created and existed either in the transaction cache or the db.
